183
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're... a Bug?</font>

184
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

185
00:15:20,850 --> 00:15:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I don't do something, the universe
