187
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, sorry. I've actually only
looped a few times so far.</font>

188
00:15:37,430 --> 00:15:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. This Setsu still doesn't
know much about the loops.</i></font>

189
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This isn't good. I'm just going to make
them more nervous talking about this.</i></font>

190
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what's going to happen?</font>

191
00:15:52,950 --> 00:15:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do?</font>

192
00:15:55,570 --> 00:15:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll just have to do your best.</font>

193
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

194
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's one thing I know.</font>

195
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to continue on an
amazing journey through the loops</font>

196
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and help everyone—me included.</font>

197
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

198
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. You've got this.</font>

199
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Believe in yourself.</font>

200
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An anomalous lifeform has been
