201
00:16:21,710 --> 00:16:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I repeat.</i></font>

202
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An anomalous lifeform has been
detected within the sick bay.</i></font>

203
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have time to be depressed.
I need to think.</i></font>

204
00:16:37,930 --> 00:16:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thankfully, there aren't any
Gnosia infectees in this loop.</i></font>

205
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means I can talk to any
of the others without worry.</i></font>

206
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:50,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With Setsu out of the question, the one
who's probably best able to help me is...</i></font>

207
00:16:53,410 --> 00:16:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've recovered already?</font>

208
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should put off the destruction
of the universe for a while.</font>

209
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But isn't this just
delaying the inevitable?</font>

210
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's important right now
is buying some time.</font>

211
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If what you said earlier is true,</font>

212
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you restart the loop,
everyone else's memory is reset.</font>

213
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you'll have to start all over again.</font>

214
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but...</font>

215
00:17:23,690 --> 00:17:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before we go any further,
I want you to show me.</font>

216
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. I guess I promised you that.</font>

217
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh... I never thought I'd get to
study a living sample like this.</font>

218
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doubt not, fear not, and know.</font>

219
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowledge will save all.</font>

220
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not responding.
It's definitely attached itself to you.</font>

221
00:17:51,450 --> 00:17:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My condolences.</font>

222
00:17:53,930 --> 00:17:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you know that I'm not lying, right?</font>

223
00:17:56,560 --> 00:18:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About the looping, and about being a Bug.</font>

224
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That does seem to be the case.</font>

225
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then, the solution
is actually quite simple.</font>

226
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

227
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ha! Do try and use your brain for once.</font>

228
00:18:08,810 --> 00:18:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been conflating
two distinct phenomena.</font>

229
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Bug version of you and the real you...</font>

230
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the two of you meet, it gives rise to
a dual existence, destroying the universe.</font>

231
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the result of one phenomenon.</font>

232
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But your continued existence is the
result of a different phenomenon—</font>

233
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the time loop you are currently
subjected to by the Silver Key.</font>

234
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two separate phenomena entirely.</font>

235
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your inability to leave this loop has
nothing to do with your status as a Bug.</font>

236
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cause is right there before you.</font>

237
00:18:41,060 --> 00:18:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

238
00:18:42,850 --> 00:18:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the looks of it,
your Silver Key isn't filled yet.</font>

239
00:18:47,390 --> 00:18:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It still thirsts for information,
which means...</font>

240
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll keep returning me to whatever world
line still has information to find...</font>

241
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">until I gain what it wants.</font>

242
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? How does it feel to be entirely
at the Silver Key's beck and call?</font>

243
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sucks.</font>

244
00:19:09,090 --> 00:19:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it hasn't been all bad.</font>

245
00:19:13,870 --> 00:19:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got to find out a lot about all of you.</font>

246
00:19:17,130 --> 00:19:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got to talk to everyone a lot,
and I've really come to like you all.</font>

247
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even you, Racio.</font>

248
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

249
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fact that I keep getting brought back
here no matter how many times I loop</i></font>

250
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>means that there's some information
that I can only gain here.</i></font>

251
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Information that I can only gain
within this short amount of time.</i></font>

252
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone I can only meet
at this exact opportunity...</i></font>

253
00:19:46,730 --> 00:19:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's it!</i></font>

254
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand?</font>

255
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not at all.</font>

256
00:20:15,530 --> 00:20:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured as much. Considering how
dated this instant learning system is.</font>

257
00:20:19,430 --> 00:20:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you get up?</font>

