00:20:47,670 --> 00:20:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I honestly don't remember...</font>

265
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, is that so?</font>

266
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I wanted to thank you.</font>

267
00:20:57,950 --> 00:20:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Chipie.</font>

268
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's thanks to you that everyone
on board was saved.</font>

269
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

270
00:21:05,410 --> 00:21:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really don't remember...</font>

271
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, the one who actually
led everyone was Setsu.</font>

272
00:21:11,530 --> 00:21:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to an eyewitness,</font>

273
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you tried to protect Setsu
back then and got hurt.</font>

274
00:21:19,740 --> 00:21:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

275
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though it doesn't seem that Setsu
realizes that you saved them either.</font>

276
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, anyway, glad you're all right.</font>

277
00:21:30,130 --> 00:21:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would've been a real downer
if you'd died after all that.</font>

278
00:21:35,780 --> 00:21:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

279
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please not tell
Setsu about this?</font>

280
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want them to worry.</font>

281
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. I'll pass that on
